Class AtlassianSynchronizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rogatio.circlead.control.synchronizer.DefaultSynchronizer
      • org.rogatio.circlead.control.synchronizer.atlassian.AtlassianSynchronizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISynchronizer
    public class AtlassianSynchronizer
extends DefaultSynchronizer
    The Class AtlassianSynchronizer synchronizes Circlead with Atlassian Confluence Server. Could be used for CLoud- and Dedicated-Server.
